name: Narberal Gamma (Overlord)
description:
It is a character LoRA of Narberal Gamma from Overlord. V1.0 was trained on AbyssOrangeMix2_hard model. V1.1 was trained on NovelAI.

To get Narberal Gamma's outfits add:

For maid outfit: "maid, black hair, apron, maid headdress, single hair bun, black eyes, maid apron"

For armored maid outfit: as maid, but add "(armor, armored dress:1.2)"

For mercenary outfit: "white shirt, long sleeves, bangs, high ponytail, (brown cape,:1.2) brown pants, head tilt, sidelocks, brown belt, belt buckle, blunt bangs"

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description: Retrained the model with larger dataset on NovelAI model following this guide: https://civitai.com/models/22530/guide-make-your-own-loras-easy-and-free
